{
  "stem": "21582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And first, they would just pick people up from the streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember my father came once home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was just, just, saying, I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't they have mothers?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't they have children?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How can they-- how can they impose such heinous, such, such terrible torture on children?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, even today when I watch television-- sometimes-- oh, when I watch my grandchildren, when I watch my grandchildren, I sometime have a shutter go through me, and I just cannot understand how they could have done-- how they could have done this to such beautiful promise.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they would come in, in battalions, sort of a double trot, their, their boots against, against, the, the cement or cobblestones.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you could here the, the, the clanking of, of, of the bayonets and guns and, and, and the triggers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And shouting, [GERMAN] Out Jews, out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and they did it with such-- with such storm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you escaped it, if they they were satisfied with, with, with their-- with what they hunted up, they would go away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then you never knew when-- where it would happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that point, the people started to disappear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that point, people started to think of, OK, the most, the most thing that was in the fore-- in your mind was, where do you hide?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So people hid under beds, between, between the blankets, between even mattresses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, you had to do it so smoothly that they wouldn't-- that you wouldn't be found.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In drawers, in cupboards, in, in, in the most unusual places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, not-- after a while, they became common knowledge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it also became a random thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
